TableView.name: POPULATION_SEGMENTS
TableView.userDefinedSQL:
SELECT ID,
DST_CODE,
DST_DESCRIPTION,
LOC_ID_COUNTRY,
LOC_NAME_COUNTRY,
ISO_COUNTRY_CODE,
UNHCR_COUNTRY_CODE,
LOC_ID_ASYLUM,
LOC_NAME_ASYLUM,
LOC_TYPE_DESCRIPTION,
LOC_ID_ORIGIN,
LOC_NAME_ORIGIN,
ISO_ORIGIN_CODE,
UNHCR_ORIGIN_CODE,
LOC_ID_SOURCE,
LOC_NAME_SOURCE,
DIM_ID1,
DIM_DESCRIPTION1,
DIM_CODE1,
DIMT_CODE1,
DIMT_DESCRIPTION1,
DIM_ID2,
DIM_DESCRIPTION2,
DIM_CODE2,
DIMT_CODE2,
DIMT_DESCRIPTION2,
DIM_ID3,
DIM_DESCRIPTION3,
DIM_CODE3,
DIMT_CODE3,
DIMT_DESCRIPTION3,
DIM_ID4,
DIM_DESCRIPTION4,
DIM_CODE4,
DIMT_CODE4,
DIMT_DESCRIPTION4,
DIM_ID5,
DIM_DESCRIPTION5,
DIM_CODE5,
DIMT_CODE5,
DIMT_DESCRIPTION5,
SEQ_NBR,
SUB_SEGMENT_NAME,
PPG_ID,
PPG_DESCRIPTION,
ITM_ID,
VERSION_NBR
FROM
(SELECT PSG.ID,
PSG.DST_CODE,
DST.DESCRIPTION AS DST_DESCRIPTION,
PSG.LOC_ID_COUNTRY,
LOC1.NAME AS LOC_NAME_COUNTRY,
LOCA1.CHAR_VALUE AS ISO_COUNTRY_CODE,
LOCA2.CHAR_VALUE AS UNHCR_COUNTRY_CODE,
PSG.LOC_ID_ASYLUM,
LOC2.NAME AS LOC_NAME_ASYLUM,
NVL(LOCTV.DESCRIPTION, LOCT.DESCRIPTION) AS LOC_TYPE_DESCRIPTION,
PSG.LOC_ID_ORIGIN,
LOC3.NAME AS LOC_NAME_ORIGIN,
LOCA3.CHAR_VALUE AS ISO_ORIGIN_CODE,
LOCA4.CHAR_VALUE AS UNHCR_ORIGIN_CODE,
PSG.LOC_ID_SOURCE,
LOC4.NAME AS LOC_NAME_SOURCE,
PSG.DIM_ID1,
DIM1.DESCRIPTION AS DIM_DESCRIPTION1,
DIM1.CODE AS DIM_CODE1,
DIM1.DIMT_CODE AS DIMT_CODE1,
DIMT1.DESCRIPTION AS DIMT_DESCRIPTION1,
PSG.DIM_ID2,
DIM2.DESCRIPTION AS DIM_DESCRIPTION2,
DIM2.CODE AS DIM_CODE2,
DIM2.DIMT_CODE AS DIMT_CODE2,
DIMT2.DESCRIPTION AS DIMT_DESCRIPTION2,
PSG.DIM_ID3,
DIM3.DESCRIPTION AS DIM_DESCRIPTION3,
DIM3.CODE AS DIM_CODE3,
DIM3.DIMT_CODE AS DIMT_CODE3,
DIMT3.DESCRIPTION AS DIMT_DESCRIPTION3,
PSG.DIM_ID4,
DIM4.DESCRIPTION AS DIM_DESCRIPTION4,
DIM4.CODE AS DIM_CODE4,
DIM4.DIMT_CODE AS DIMT_CODE4,
DIMT4.DESCRIPTION AS DIMT_DESCRIPTION4,
PSG.DIM_ID5,
DIM5.DESCRIPTION AS DIM_DESCRIPTION5,
DIM5.CODE AS DIM_CODE5,
DIM5.DIMT_CODE AS DIMT_CODE5,
DIMT5.DESCRIPTION AS DIMT_DESCRIPTION5,
PSG.SEQ_NBR,
TXT.TEXT AS SUB_SEGMENT_NAME,
PSG.PPG_ID,
PPG.DESCRIPTION AS PPG_DESCRIPTION,
PSG.ITM_ID,
PSG.VERSION_NBR
FROM T_POPULATION_SEGMENTS PSG
LEFT OUTER JOIN DISPLACEMENT_STATUSES DST
ON DST.CODE = PSG.DST_CODE
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATIONS LOC1
ON LOC1.ID = PSG.LOC_ID_COUNTRY
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATION_ATTRIBUTES LOCA1
ON LOCA1.LOC_ID = LOC1.ID
AND LOCA1.LOCAT_CODE = 'IS03166A3'
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATION_ATTRIBUTES LOCA2
ON LOCA2.LOC_ID = LOC1.ID
AND LOCA2.LOCAT_CODE = 'HCRCC'
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATIONS LOC2
ON LOC2.ID = PSG.LOC_ID_ASYLUM
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATION_TYPES LOCT
ON LOCT.CODE = LOC2.LOCT_CODE
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATION_TYPE_VARIANTS LOCTV
ON LOCTV.ID = LOC2.LOCTV_ID
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATIONS LOC3
ON LOC3.ID = PSG.LOC_ID_ORIGIN
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATION_ATTRIBUTES LOCA3
ON LOCA3.LOC_ID = LOC3.ID
AND LOCA3.LOCAT_CODE = 'IS03166A3'
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATION_ATTRIBUTES LOCA4
ON LOCA4.LOC_ID = LOC3.ID
AND LOCA4.LOCAT_CODE = 'HCRCC'
LEFT OUTER JOIN LOCATIONS LOC4
ON LOC4.ID = PSG.LOC_ID_SOURCE
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_VALUES DIM1
ON DIM1.ID = PSG.DIM_ID1
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_TYPES DIMT1
ON DIMT1.CODE = DIM1.DIMT_CODE
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_VALUES DIM2
ON DIM2.ID = PSG.DIM_ID2
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_TYPES DIMT2
ON DIMT2.CODE = DIM2.DIMT_CODE
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_VALUES DIM3
ON DIM3.ID = PSG.DIM_ID3
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_TYPES DIMT3
ON DIMT3.CODE = DIM3.DIMT_CODE
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_VALUES DIM4
ON DIM4.ID = PSG.DIM_ID4
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_TYPES DIMT4
ON DIMT4.CODE = DIM4.DIMT_CODE
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_VALUES DIM5
ON DIM5.ID = PSG.DIM_ID5
LEFT OUTER JOIN DIMENSION_TYPES DIMT5
ON DIMT5.CODE = DIM5.DIMT_CODE
LEFT OUTER JOIN POPULATION_PLANNING_GROUPS PPG
ON PPG.ID = PSG.PPG_ID
LEFT OUTER JOIN TEXT_ITEMS TXT
ON TXT.ITM_ID = PSG.ITM_ID
AND TXT.TXTT_CODE = 'PSSGNAME'
AND TXT.SEQ_NBR = 1
)
